{"tid":2141334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府譴責騷擾內地檢測支援先遣隊人員的行為","createTime":"2020-08-05T14:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T15:36:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0d520ee509d437d08b5db63fbcb10dccc7aab7","tid":2141334,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542057-20200805.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542057-20200805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2FzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=04a34bf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542057-20200805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7615eeca\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542057-20200805.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府譴責連日來有非建制派區議員及個別人士，到內地核酸檢測先遣隊成員入住酒店及考察地點示威，騷擾先遣隊員，又重申特區政府感謝中央支持特區的抗疫工作，並迅速派先遣人員來港進行有關工作。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，本港疫情嚴峻，社會理應上下一心，齊心抗疫，然而有部分人士卻罔顧公眾利益和衞生安全，做出分化行為，並試圖抺黑、破壞中央協助支援香港對抗疫情的工作，特區政府對此等行為予以嚴厲譴責，又呼籲社會大眾認清一小撮近年不斷散播「反內地」言論人士的政治圖謀，他們借中央支援特區抗疫再次挑起矛盾，是罔顧香港疫情嚴峻和市民的健康。<br />\n  <br />\n發言人重申，這次中央是應特區政府請求而派遣人員來港支援防疫抗疫工作，先遣隊員連日的考察是為與特區政府共同制定加強檢測的能力，以便為擴大社區檢測計劃做好準備，相關人員來港的所有安排均符合法律要求，不存在任何所謂的「政治考慮」。"},{"pid":"30a15ae6029db1cc194ffce83d7c4128f9314eba","tid":2141334,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:55:45.000Z","msg":"香港同中國一樣示威都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a143b3453d1cafdb1a6d4ffafac605467295aab6","tid":2141334,"uid":36152,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"點樣擾亂呀？"},{"pid":"fce77a54376816bb4bec78973ffd8e42c5a0cddd","tid":2141334,"uid":254594,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"D本來好嚴重既字眼用到爛哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜鳩都譴責<br />\n已經同表示關注同一lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afe2f0a8f2b5f5986cb7a36a2da32ed115319f1","tid":2141334,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"效忠基本法示威自由"},{"pid":"c316eb87c3ec7b95207b601cd82604491e7d7749","tid":2141334,"uid":215611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"一日譴責幾十次<br />\n你唔煩我都覺得煩啦"},{"pid":"3f5e7ab81ab8b6125679db6e9c464e040cb070d3","tid":2141334,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"佢地有牌未<br />\n有冇工作visa <br />\n真係當自己天行者, 唔撚使得到香港醫療制度認可<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港無呢d 人？香港開埠百幾年<br />\n唔識起臨時醫院, 唔識開臨時實驗室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪撚玩啦<br />\n庫房咁多錢唔用返比本地人才, <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">借d 易要hk人接受內地醫療 </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d137d355aaeabab2ff6dd29392eb3087874c6673","tid":2141334,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"開槍呀"},{"pid":"bc62d8a24ba1fa147669f88b5a8b8fbb6d954474","tid":2141334,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:14:39.000Z","msg":"躝屍趷路啦你哋d中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d696fcfd176cbdc18db6662b605485798d8076e","tid":2141334,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"嘜嘢叫建制非建制，<br />\n去抗議嘅都係愛港，都係建制派。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3ae33711863690c4ee202029d0a1dbad3fd276","tid":2141334,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"躝返支那,大家都高興"}]}